author: stahlleiton
body:
#### PR description:

This PR adds the following relvals to test the use of NANOAOD:
- 183.01: 2026 PbPb UPC MC workflow
- 144.903: 2026 PbPb UPC data workflow

This will be useful to eventually adapt NANOAOD for the use in heavy ion data taking.

@mandrenguyen 

#### PR validation:

Tested with relvals 183.01,144.903
title: Add NANO PbPb UPC relvals
